068032】<br />\n<a href=\"http://dama420.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdama420.blogspot.com%2F&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7f37183d\" target=\"_blank\">http://dama420.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n大麻种子出售【Q1966033】的博客<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://98586263.home.news.cn/blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F98586263.home.news.cn%2Fblog%2F&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=52317e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://98586263.home.news.cn/blog/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n出售大麻种子<br />\n<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/101433758111246984572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F101433758111246984572&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=797d9dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/101433758111246984572</a>"},{"pid":"180a85da73a1b67a6a844ab362b47a7bb50c25d5","tid":973312,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bda1d1517371077c87e78c7c06de6269ae66d63","tid":973312,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"香港對thc含量係唔係0容忍，無min threshold?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"藏有種子是合法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab382da9e4cb02cf1352a0967180d304742359ed","tid":973312,"uid":215603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:12:53.000Z","msg":"泰國批准藥用大麻合法化被譽為民眾的「新年禮物」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2251271/org/dd232f0eb46834c4d08929f01903bdb8.JPG/zPbn6zGw5q_2an8FJqEMrncBLg8OuSalwjz1GMI89Rg?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2251271%2Forg%2Fdd232f0eb46834c4d08929f01903bdb8.JPG%2FzPbn6zGw5q_2an8FJqEMrncBLg8OuSalwjz1GMI89Rg%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=fad42370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國國會周二（25日）表決通過容許當地使用大麻作為醫療用途，是東南亞地區首個國家批准大麻合法化，有議員形容今次立法是為民眾帶來「新年禮物」。<br />\n<br />\n泰國軍政府組成的國會通過修改《1979年麻醉藥物法》，據《曼谷郵報》報道，消費者只要有醫生處方或證明，就可擁有指定數量的大麻作為醫療用途。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，當局將會嚴格管制生產及出售大麻，<br />\n<br />\n以及東南亞常用的草本類興奮劑「卡痛」（Kratom）。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指，國會為了可以在新年前通過法案，特意加開會議，並等待政府刊憲後正式生效。國會法律起草委員會主席Somchai Sawangkarn表示，這是國會為泰國政府和民眾帶來的新年禮物。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/世界說/275375/泰國批准藥用大麻合法化-被譽為民眾的-新年禮物\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA%2F275375%2F%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E8%97%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E5%8C%96-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%BD%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%9A%84-%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A6%AE%E7%89%A9&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d097b8bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/世界說/275375/泰國批准藥用大麻合法化-被譽為民眾的-新年禮物</a>"},{"pid":"60defc8a1a013b4992d8b1630a49b38fc9d631a8","tid":973312,"uid":215603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"可口可樂擬與加拿大大麻製造商　研發大麻飲品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1877748/org/63634617e92fd7e73b84ed730d53c7c2.jpg/2tnZdWBkgbfx_yoQq84FzQxYDHBJDvIoRXgMUkV4DFI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1877748%2Forg%2F63634617e92fd7e73b84ed730d53c7c2.jpg%2F2tnZdWBkgbfx_yoQq84FzQxYDHBJDvIoRXgMUkV4DFI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=be23304e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報道，可口可樂正在與加拿大大麻製造商Aurora Cannabis進行協商，有意共同研發含大麻成份的飲品。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂並未透露有新研發的飲品，僅表示公司內部與許多飲品業者相同，都有在關注大麻二酚（Cannabidiol）加入飲料的可行性。<br />\n<br />\nAurora大麻公司則表示，的確有計畫進軍飲品市場。大麻二酚是大麻中不會影響精神行為的成分，可用於緩解疼痛，卻不會讓人精神亢奮。<br />\n<br />\n成份不影響精神行為　有止痛作用<br />\n知情人士表示，該款飲品會以健康為導向，並有消炎、舒緩肌肉痙攣、止痛等功能，不過雙方談判只是處於初步階段，<br />\n<br />\n該款飲品是否會成功問世仍是未知數，可口可樂亦正在與其他公司談論潛在的合作可能。<br />\n為應對汽水銷售放緩的問題，可口可樂正不斷拓展業務。早前可口可樂宣布收購連鎖咖啡店Costa。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有傳可口可樂收購葛蘭素史克（Glaxosmithkline）在印度的好立克（Horlicks）業務。"},{"pid":"5c98b9ac53d4b93a76c73e3c25954024195900e6","tid":973312,"uid":6026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ac735df6f4198130236389147ae2ac7450d1b0b","tid":973312,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢 不會死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"種大麻<br />\n無論雨怎麼打 大麻仍是會開花"},{"pid":"88355ab7417582f1f74ec8ad09042d971c755e6c","tid":973312,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"難唔難種?"},{"pid":"f9c16d31c4899078a640cff5462f82d6d80d6b95","tid":973312,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88355ab7417582f1f74ec8ad09042d971c755e6c","tid":973312,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"難唔難種?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"野火燒不盡,春風吹又生"},{"pid":"d741d989222c4366dc83a368eeaa4b5268b5c8e9","tid":973312,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88355ab7417582f1f74ec8ad09042d971c755e6c","tid":973312,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"難唔難種?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔難 <br />\n種得靚就難"},{"pid":"8eb0e9ee5da796ca9726d1c549aa97e989a30e22","tid":973312,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d741d989222c4366dc83a368eeaa4b5268b5c8e9","tid":973312,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88355ab7417582f1f74ec8ad09042d971c755e6c","tid":973312,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"難唔難種?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔難 <br />\n種得靚就難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"種到棵聖誕樹咁 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}